References: <20090617194628.994fn5ugrowokg08@webmail.fhcrc.org>	<4A39DB90.804@cbs.dtu.dk>	<20090618001124.kntq2idk84co8sg8@webmail.fhcrc.org>	<4A3A17FA.5020206@cbs.dtu.dk>
